    </select>
    <copy name="eca5" prop="evaluatedCellA5" tname="encrypt" />
    <copy name="ctext" tname="eca5" prop="text" />
  </setup>

  <p>
    For this exercise, you will encrypt the following short, famous song opening using the shift cipher.
    Enter the associated ciphertext (all capital letters, please!), using the plaintext chosen from
    opening lines from famous songs.
    <me>\text{Plaintext: $pt} \quad::\quad \text{Encryption Key: $key}.</me>
    <alert>Hint:</alert> You can go back to the previous page, use your assigned key, and use the table there to perform the operation.
  </p>
  <p>
    Ciphertext:
    <answer type="text">
        $ctext
    </answer>
  </p>
</module>
